-- Bank of France to Re-Pay Greece EU754 Million Interest on Bonds
-- B y   M a r k   D e e n
-- 2012-07-04T15:12:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-04/bank-of-france-to-re-pay-greece-eu754-million-interest-on-bonds.html
The Bank of France will hand over 754
million euros ($944 million) of interest collected on Greek
 government bonds  it holds as part of agreements to offer the
country financial support. The figure was given today by the
French treasury in its revised 2012 budget.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mark Deen in Paris at 
